body_html:
It looks like it's looking for this file: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tensorboard/TAG
which (in my case) was actually not present in the /tensorboard directory.

After creating a file called "TAG" with the content "22" (which was the content in the master branch when I looked it up) everything worked fine.

body:
It looks like it's looking for this file: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tensorboard/TAG
which (in my case) was actually not present in the /tensorboard directory.

After **creating a file called "TAG" with the content "22"** (which was the content in the master branch when I looked it up) everything worked fine.
